1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,060
You are fired. Those were the words I received
after 18 years of dedication to Novus Tech,

2
00:00:05,060 --> 00:00:10,780
spoken by Julian Vance, the founder's arrogant
31-year-old MBA son, with a smug grin on his face.

3
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:14,780
He called me expensive overhead, pointed
to the glass door, and told me to get out.

4
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:19,220
I did not raise my voice. I did not make a
scene. I just packed my favorite coffee mug,

5
00:00:19,380 --> 00:00:23,020
walked out of the building, and smiled.
As the glass doors closed behind me,

6
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:24,380
I knew the countdown had started.
